==Useful info==
'''Deep elf archers''' are skilled ranged fighters who can also cast a few [[Hexes]]. They can be found in the [[Elven Halls]]. They also occasionally appear elsewhere.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*As they have [[Repel Missiles]], fighting them in a ranged duel is less effective than usual (but not impossible). Ways to lower their [[EV]], such as [[BVC]] or a [[wand of roots]], are effective if you try to do so.
*Their hexes aren't as dangerous as the likes of [[orc sorcerer]]s or [[deep elf high priest]]s, but if you don't have good [[willpower]], you should keep them in mind.

==History==
{{CBA|0.32|deep elf archers will have [[Blink Range]] instead of [[Blink Away]].}}
*Deep elf archers were introduced in [[0.18]].

